title: Meet our people – Piers Jalland,  Investment Manager | frasersproperty.com.au
description: As Investment Manager, Piers and the Investments team oversee Frasers Property's retail and office assets - from acquisition and reporting through to budgeting and analysis. Piers was drawn to Frasers Property by its professionalism, approach to challenges, and investment in its people. The team I was working with in 2018, versus the team I am working with now, are all still the same team members but they're in very different roles - I think that's a reflection of the retention and opportunities you get when you work at Frasers._Welcome to the Red Chair series, in which we pull back the curtains to reveal some of the personalities and characters at Frasers Property Australia and find out what belonging to our company means to them. These are the diverse people which shape our business, the dynamic atmosphere we inhabit, the culture we enjoy, and the game-changing projects we deliver. By understanding what drives them and where their passions lie, we gain new insights into what it means to be a Frasers Property person.
